datasets.name: dataset_17
queryLines: SELECT Home_Tile AS Home_Tile, MEASURE(f_ctr) AS Percent_Home_Tile_Clicked_vs_Homepage_Displayed, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Tile_Views) AS Total_Unique_Tile_Views, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Tile_Clicks) AS Total_Unique_Tile_Clicks, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Interstitial_Views) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Views, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Interstitial_Primary_Button_Clicks) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Primary_Button_Clicks, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Interstitial_Secondary_Button_Clicks) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Secondary_Button_Clicks FROM hpx_events_model_homepage_summary GROUP BY Home_Tile ORDER BY f_ctr DESC

value.displayName: % Home Tile Clicked Vs Homepage Displayed
